shuva also ( bengali : সুভা ) is a bangladeshi bengali-language film , released in 2006 all over bangladesh .   it is directed by chashi nazrul islam .   the story is based on rabindra nath thakur 's novel shuvashini .   the film was produced and distributed by impress telefilm ltd . it stars shakib khan , purnima , chashi nazrul islam and sujata .   shakib khan and purnima receive the highest accolades for their performance .